&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 83&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;# There are a few important trade-offs here:
